Welcome badminton back into your busy schedule. With the refreshingly no strings 'Pay & Play' sessions, it's all about convenient court times without the need to commit to any future involvement.

No Strings brings you the chance to turn up and play with like minded people, so no need to find yourself a partner. Previous experience is not necessary no is any equipment as these coached sessions are an enjoyable way to take part in the sport.
Organised sessions with all the equipment provided and guidance if needed.
